# @{{name}}/tsconfig

Shared TypeScript configuration for the monorepo.

## Usage

Packages extend the base configuration in their `tsconfig.json`:

```json
{
  "extends": "@{{name}}/tsconfig/base.json",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "rootDir": ".",
    "outDir": "dist"
  },
  "include": ["src"]
}
```

## Configuration

The `base.json` provides strict TypeScript settings optimized for Effect-based applications with ESNext target and bundler module resolution.
